{"tid":1898700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【發大財】星之子陳易希公司開放網上平台 助學校停課不停學","createTime":"2020-02-26T07:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T09:19:37.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"89909473f84afb08bb40a041c240abf7140ca1cb","tid":1898700,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:51:25.000Z","msg":"遇沙士停課 得老師相助續研機械人<br />\n<br />\n校家角智能校園方案行政總裁陳易希亦是大眾熟悉的「星之子」。他憶述，2003年仍是一名初中生，當時埋首於製作機械人，惟遇上「沙士」同樣面對停課，幸而有老師扶助，亦開放實驗室予他，才可繼續研發，奪得國際大獎。<br />\n<br />\n17年過去，受到武漢肺炎疫情影響，全港所有學校停課近兩個月。陳易希表示，新年起疫情嚴峻，「不斷喺度諗做到咩可以幫到社會，睇下自己公司有冇嘢啱」。他們花一個星期時間，將2016年的推出智慧校園網上平台「校家角」升級，期望更多人可受惠。<br />\n<br />\n港人團隊製作 整合多項功能<br />\n<br />\n陳易希指，系統設「校園電視台」，老師可上載拍下的教學片段、工作紙，學生只要登入系統便可瀏覽，做完後便能交功課，校方又能透過即時聊天室回饋。他解釋，系統其中一大特點是，整合了多個程式功能，「不少學校面對資訊混亂情況，如果逐樣逐樣分開做，工作量會上升」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，平台由本地團隊研發，校方、家長遇到任何使用困難，團隊可迅速解答，現時有約100間學校使用，一日訊息量可高達30萬。陳透露，有計劃添置LIVE直播功能。<br />\n<br />\n幼稚園透過程式 照常辦才藝表演比賽<br />\n<br />\n加州天地幼稚園校長文敬群表示，學校使用平台已接近兩年，上年受社會運動影響，亦曾停課兩周，當時老師自製影片，以致學生在家自學。惟其坦言，是次停課時間長，校方很難評核學生的學習進度。她認為，透過平台正正整合校方需要，現時仍可舉行「才藝表演比賽」，同學拍片放上平台比拼；老師亦能拍教學片段，指導同學準備畢業禮。<br />\n<br />\n文認為，同其他類似平台最大分別是，系統無需披露個人電話號碼，但家長、老師能做到「24小時的聯繫」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4039251/org/9fa436425603c6659232816d68dd4f88.jpg/ePbKvz2ph-AXMu-IT1Qi8lPf0JP0hmuiL13zNAVd8zQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4039251%2Forg%2F9fa436425603c6659232816d68dd4f88.jpg%2FePbKvz2ph-AXMu-IT1Qi8lPf0JP0hmuiL13zNAVd8zQ&h=430f9ba8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d86fd2f3090a89f75d887a70e49347d143837f9","tid":1898700,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">響大家研究錢唔錢的時候<br />\n特衰政府已經清算手足</span><br />\nHA 清算罷工醫護<br />\n外媒記者報道<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=4051e9fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&h=f38fff00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ezracheungtoto/status/1232556910894649345?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fezracheungtoto%2Fstatus%2F1232556910894649345%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=d6bed761\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fezracheungtoto%2Fstatus%2F1232556910894649345%3Fs%3D21&h=caebb208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ezracheungtoto/status/1232556910894649345?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n香港記者報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sumlokkei/status/1232554841500569600?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsumlokkei%2Fstatus%2F1232554841500569600%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=4b50daaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsumlokkei%2Fstatus%2F1232554841500569600%3Fs%3D21&h=d0ba2080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sumlokkei/status/1232554841500569600?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/damon_pang/status/1232558018920767495?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdamon_pang%2Fstatus%2F1232558018920767495%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=0615adbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdamon_pang%2Fstatus%2F1232558018920767495%3Fs%3D21&h=3495ed47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/damon_pang/status/1232558018920767495?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">政府話手足被捕現場叫名都當呈堂證明在現場</